<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Security Awareness Training</title><style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea 0%,#764ba2 100%);min-height:100vh;padding:2rem}.training-container{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;background:white;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)}.header{background:#e74c3c;color:white;padding:2rem;text-align:center}.header-icon{font-size:4rem;margin-bottom:1rem}.content{padding:3rem}h1{color:#2c3e50;margin-bottom:1rem}.alert{background:#fff3cd;border-left:4px solid #ffc107;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;border-radius:4px}.section{margin-bottom:2rem}.section h2{color:#2c3e50;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:1.25rem}.indicators{background:#f8f9fa;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:1.5rem}.indicator-item{display:flex;margin-bottom:1rem;align-items:flex-start}.indicator-icon{margin-right:1rem;font-size:1.5rem}.quiz{background:#e8f5e9;padding:2rem;border-radius:8px;margin-top:2rem}.quiz-question{margin-bottom:1.5rem}.quiz-option{padding:1rem;background:white;margin-bottom:0.5rem;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid transparent;transition:all 0.2s}.quiz-option:hover{border-color:#4caf50}.quiz-option.selected{border-color:#4caf50;background:#f1f8e9}.btn{padding:1rem 2rem;background:#27ae60;color:white;border:none;border-radius:4px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;width:100%;margin-top:1rem}.btn:hover{background:#229954}.success-message{background:#d4edda;color:#155724;padding:2rem;text-align:center;border-radius:8px;display:none}</style></head><body><div class="training-container"><div class="header"><div class="header-icon">⚠️</div><h1 style="color:white;font-size:2rem;">This Was A Security Test</h1><p style="margin-top:1rem;">The message you received was a phishing simulation</p></div><div class="content"><div class="alert"><strong>Hello <%= employeeName %>,</strong><br>The message you received about "<%= campaignName %>" was not real. This was a controlled training exercise conducted by our Security Team to help you recognize sophisticated phishing attempts.</div><div class="section"><h2>What You Should Have Noticed</h2><div class="indicators"><div class="indicator-item"><div class="indicator-icon">❌</div><div><strong>Authority Exploitation:</strong> Executive-level requests for credential actions are unusual and should always be verified through trusted channels.</div></div><div class="indicator-item"><div class="indicator-icon">❌</div><div><strong>Timing Pressure:</strong> Urgent deadlines for unannounced initiatives create pressure to act without thinking.</div></div><div class="indicator-item"><div class="indicator-icon">❌</div><div><strong>Process Deviation:</strong> Legitimate system access validation doesn't require proactive login through email links.</div></div><div class="indicator-item"><div class="indicator-icon">❌</div><div><strong>Domain Mismatch:</strong> The sender's email address didn't match our organization's actual domain.</div></div></div></div><div class="section"><h2>What You Should Do Next Time</h2><ol style="margin-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.8;"><li><strong>Don't click links</strong> in unexpected emails requesting credentials</li><li><strong>Verify independently</strong> by contacting IT or the supposed sender through known channels</li><li><strong>Report suspicious messages</strong> using the "Report Phish" button</li><li><strong>Trust your instincts</strong> - if something feels off, it probably is</li></ol></div><div class="quiz"><h2 style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Quick Knowledge Check</h2><div class="quiz-question"><p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:1rem;">If you receive an urgent email from a senior executive requesting you to click a link and enter your credentials, what should you do first?</p><div class="quiz-option" data-answer="correct">Contact the executive or IT through known channels to verify the request</div><div class="quiz-option">Click the link to see if it looks legitimate</div><div class="quiz-option">Reply to the email asking if it's real</div><div class="quiz-option">Forward it to colleagues to get their opinion</div></div><button class="btn" onclick="submitQuiz()">Submit Answer</button></div><div class="success-message" id="successMessage"><h2 style="color:#155724;margin-bottom:1rem;">✅ Training Complete!</h2><p>Thank you for completing this security awareness training. Remember: staying vigilant protects everyone.</p><p style="margin-top:1rem;"><strong>Questions?</strong> Contact the Security Team at security@organization.edu</p></div></div></div><script>let selectedAnswer=null;document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-option').forEach(option=>{option.addEventListener('click',function(){document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-option').forEach(o=>o.classList.remove('selected'));this.classList.add('selected');selectedAnswer=this.dataset.answer})});function submitQuiz(){if(!selectedAnswer){alert('Please select an answer');return}const score=selectedAnswer==='correct'?100:0;fetch('/training/<%= token %>/complete',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({score})}).then(res=>res.json()).then(data=>{if(data.success){document.querySelector('.quiz').style.display='none';document.getElementById('successMessage').style.display='block'}})}</script></body></html>
